sections[5]{title,body}:
  Objective,Turn the repository into a reproducible proof program for local-first genomics agents with separate evidence for benchmark correctness, interpretation discipline, public-demo usefulness, and cross-harness portability.
  DatasetOrder,Use synthetic fixtures first then HG002 then CMRG then one Harvard PGP public sample then 1000 Genomes then interpretation and reasoning packs.
  ProofArtifacts,Ship an HG002 benchmark page, a CMRG scorecard, one public genome walkthrough, one interpretation evaluation pack, and a CLI provenance demo.
  Constraints,Keep genome data local by default, never present output as diagnosis, and keep PRS or exploratory signals separate from direct variant findings.
  Status,Active plan captured in ROADMAP.md with live execution tracked in Beads and exported to .beads/issues.jsonl. DEMO_BACKLOG.md remains shaping context only.
